message.entry: The MultiSelect parameter value must be a character vector specifying on/off.
The Location parameter value must be a 2 element vector.
TITLE argument must be a character vector.
STARTPATH argument must be a character vector.
FILTERSPEC argument must be a character vector or an M by 1 or M by 2 cell array.
All elements of FILTERSPEC cell array must be character vectors.
File argument must be a character vector.
Both X and Y arguments must be specified for the position.
This syntax has been obsoleted. Please refer to help or documentation for new syntax.
